title: Corner 3 Bedroom 2 Bath With Lots Of Natural Sunlight!
posting_body: ['Live on the Park.', ' Urban comforts, outdoor living right.', 'Wander trails along the waterfront.', 'Wrap yourself in luxury.', 'Wake up every day to the wild-hearted beauty of the Pacific Northwest – it’s right outside your window at Bell Marymoor Park.', 'From our free-spirited rooftop deck to the light-filled arboretum, every element is designed to enhance your indoor/outdoor lifestyle.', 'Roam far in your own backyard when you live next door to Marymoor Park, an immense green playground for recreation and relaxation.', 'We’re directly on the bike trail and just a few minutes away from Downtown Redmond and East Lake Sammamish.', '-Light-filled arboretum: opening to the largest backyard in redmond', '-Bocce ball, shuffle board, life-sized scrabble and mega jenga', '-Reading coves throughout community', '-Storage units available', '-24-hour fitness studio', '-24-hour package lockers', '-Tide laundry lockers', '-Rooftop grilling stations, bar, fireplace and sun-nooks', '-Generous Closet Space', '-Quartz Countertops', '-Complimentary starbucks coffee machine', '-Close proximity to burke-gilman trail', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing and Specials subject to change daily and restrictions may apply.', 'Please contact leasing agent for details.']
